data.title: David Murray in New York at Blue Note Jazz Club
data.meta_description: Check out David Murray at Blue Note Jazz Club in New York on March 01, 2022 and get detailed info for the event - tickets, photos, video and reviews.
data.text:
Musician Lineup:

David Murray: sax, bass clarinet

Dave Burrell : piano

Rashaan Carter, bass

Russel Carter: drums

As mandated by The City of New York, Blue Note New York will require proof of vaccination from all customers, staff and musicians who enter the venue. Proof of vaccination may include a physical card or digital photo of the card from the CDC, NYC Covid Safe App or the NYS Excelsior Pass. Children under 12, who cannot be vaccinated, must wear masks. In addition to the vaccination policy, New York City continues to encourage masks for all indoor gatherings, except while you are actively eating and drinking.

$5 minimum spend on food and beverage required

Full Bar & Dinner Menu Available

Seating is First Come, First Served. Arrive early for the best seats. Parties arriving separately or late are not gauranteed to be sat at the same table.

Table Seating is All-Ages, 21+ at the Bar. Please do not purchase Bar Area tickets if you are not 21 years old. Your ticket will not be honored.
